Type "breach --protocol ICE-9 --target megacorp.subnet.42"
Sleep 1200ms
Enter

Hide
Type `printf '\n\033[38;2;0;229;255m◎\033[0m Initiating ICE-9 breach sequence...\n\033[38;2;105;240;174m✓\033[0m Firewall layer 1/3 bypassed\n\033[38;2;105;240;174m✓\033[0m Firewall layer 2/3 bypassed\n\033[38;2;105;240;174m✓\033[0m Firewall layer 3/3 bypassed\n\033[38;2;0;229;255m◎\033[0m Root access obtained. Exfiltrating data...\n'` Enter
